gtkmm: gtkmm (C++ Bindings for Gtk+2)
gtkmm: 
gtkmm: gtkmm is the official C++ interface for the popular GUI library GTK+2.
gtkmm: Highlights include typesafe callbacks, and a comprehensive set of 
gtkmm: widgets that are easily extensible via inheritance. You can create user 
gtkmm: interfaces either in code or with the Glade User Interface designer, 
gtkmm: using libglademm. There's extensive documentation, including API 
gtkmm: reference and a tutorial.  gtkmm is free software distributed under LGPL.
gtkmm: 
